Detailed Description

Takes care of the job logging for packets and replies.

Usage: 

 JobLogger logger( 1, incomingQueue );
 // start a scope with new logging
 {
    JobLogger::LogScope scope( logger, incomingPacket, reply );
    // log prefix here
    // do stuff
 }
 // no log prefix here.
